Title: Series: Fasti di Napoleone
Description: Plate 14: Bonaparte's Egyptian campaign showing his troops arriving in ships and landing on shore in Egypt, and marching towards the right Engraving
Curator's comments: For comment on series see 1872,0113.684.1. This is the first of five plates on the Egyptian campaign. See "Mito e storia nei 'Fasti di Napoleone' di Andrea Appiani", Rome, 1986, n.xiv
Associated names: Associated with: Napoléon I, Emperor of the French (Napoleon)
Associated events: Associated Event: Napoleon's campaign in Egypt 1798-1799
